latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I hope you guys love @augustinusbader as much as I do and enjoy this tutorial. I’m kind of an expert now, so if you have any questions, leave them in the comments and I’ll be answering them. 💅🏻 

I used The Cream Cleansing Gel: A gentle cleanser that combines Bader’s exclusive skin care technology with powerful active botanicals to purify, revitalize, calm, and refresh. Non-foaming and formulated for all skin types. I used The Exfoliating Toner/The Essence: A 3-in-1 formula that combines the properties of a mild chemical exfoliant, a toner, and an essence to reveal smoother, softer, and more hydrated skin.
I used The Face Oil: Ultra-potent and fast-absorbing. Supports cellular renewal, nourishes, and refines the skin to deliver long-lasting radiance. Formulated for all skin types. Can be used on its own or blended with your Augustinus Bader cream.
I used The Cream: Lightweight and hydrating. Supports cellular renewal and leaves skin looking fresh, plump, even, and more radiant. Ideal for combination to oily skin types, blemish-prone skin, and as a refreshing hydrator in more humid climates.
I used The Body Oil: Nourishes, smooths, and firms for vibrant, healthier-looking skin. Silky and rich, yet fast-absorbing and non-greasy – perfect for worry-free application.
I used The Body Lotion: Soothes, firms, and addresses imperfections. Locks in moisture to revive the skin. Airy and fast-absorbing - the perfect lightweight lotion.
